data.description: Very nice 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 1 car garage town home in Estancia.This property is in a gated community and comes equip with stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, new washer, and dryer on the second level, newer hot water heater was replaced in 2019. Community features a pool for your enjoyment. Excellent location minutes from shopping, dining and the I-95. Very well-maintained community. Easy to show.
